Standard .gitignore file for a MERN stack application.

--------------------------------------------------------

1. CRITICAL SECRETS & ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES

--------------------------------------------------------

NEVER commit the .env file containing database URIs or API keys!

.env

--------------------------------------------------------

2. DEPENDENCIES

--------------------------------------------------------

Ignore the node module directories in both the root and the client/server folders.

node_modules
/client/node_modules
/server/node_modules

--------------------------------------------------------

3. BUILD OUTPUT & TEMP FILES

--------------------------------------------------------

Output of the React build process (production assets)

The Express server will serve this folder when deployed.

/client/build
/client/dist
/dist

Logs

npm-debug.log
yarn-error.log
/server/logs/

--------------------------------------------------------

4. OS & EDITOR Files

--------------------------------------------------------

.DS_Store # macOS system files
.vscode/ # VS Code workspace/settings (optional, sometimes useful to share)
*.sublime-workspace
